# BEAM VM tuning for production

## Schedulers: 0:0 uses as many as online logical processors
+S 0:0

## Increase async threads for file I/O and DNS
+A 128

## Reduce busy-wait spinning to save CPU under load
+sbwt none

## Allow plenty of Erlang processes
+P 2097152

# Optional: keep kernel poll enabled (usually default)
+K true

# You can pass additional flags at runtime via ERL_AFLAGS
